<A>__{the church is packed. close on the rings as the priest holds them aloft. if those rings could talk... jack shoots a quick look at miles, who looks right back. the priest continues his blessing.}
<L>__{exterior armenian church day}
<A>__{at the top of the stairs the wedding families greet the exiting guests in a receiving line. smiling and exuberant, jack seems utterly at home as the new groom. at the bottom of the steps miles watches the scene, not without melancholy. then }
