<D>__{hey, miles.}
<A>__{miles turns and looks up to see victoria, standing one step above him. just behind her is her new husband. he exudes the quiet confidence of a successful businessman who played college football, takes expensive skiing and sailing vacations, and hasn't read a novel since high school.}
